*DESCRIPTION_START
Milky white eyes gaze dispassionately out from gaunt, deathly pale features as
this strange being examines the world around it. Colorless silken hair flows
down its back nearly to the ground, stirring with faint rustling whispers when
it turns its head. Long, sharply pointed ears show through the shifting mane
when they swivel to detect a new sound. Voluminous robes of a mysterious
silvery-white fabric obscure further details of race and gender. 
*DESCRIPTION_END
