*DESCRIPTION_START
It is literally impossible to make a fixed description of this bizarre being,
other than the fact that it remains vaguely humanoid. Most of the time. Its
limbs, shape, and even size are in a constant state of change. Amazingly, this
seems not to cause it any discomfort, nor hinder its erratic movements in any
noticeable way whatsoever.
*DESCRIPTION_END
STRENGTH 99
MANA 250
SPELLUSE 10
