TEXM A rogue shape careens
TEXG What seemed like an ordinary object suddenly turns out to be a rogue shape.
TEXI A rogue shape's fluid form simply parts around the weapon.
TEX1 A rogue shape grows and loses several random body parts in rapid succession.
TEX2 Eyes grow in the back of a rogue shape's head, rather than turning to look.
TEXD dissolves into noxious slime that quickly seeps into the ground.
TEXA A rogue shape lurches toward
TEXR A rogue shape shrieks and backpedals away from its opponent.
TEXF Wailing, a rogue shape staggers
TEXS Some tentacles on a rogue shape contort in the gestures of preparing a spell.
TEXL Power shudders through a rogue shape as it casts its enchantment
TEXQ A rogue shape flails a few limbs in frustration.
