    AFFECT JABROOM
    ECHO ALL ...and when it clears, your surroundings have shifted. 
    STRCVT 2 JABROOM
    GMMSG A group has been moved to %2.
    AFFECT 3306
  ENDIF
  IFVAR RNUM = 3315
    ECHO ALL There is a slight shimmer in the air...
    MOVEALL JABROOM
    AFFECT JABROOM
    ECHO ALL ...and when it clears, your surroundings have shifted.
    STRCVT 2 JABROOM
    GMMSG A group has been moved to %2.
