;
;
;Da Mane Event!
; 
VARIABLE JAB2NDROOM
;
NUMBER 3300 
NAME Miasma
REGION 15
CHANNEL 72  
ASTRAL
EXIT W 3301
;
CALL 19    
;
*DESCRIPTION_START 
Tendrils of mist rise from all sides, though there seem to be no walls, no 
floor, no trees, nothing to mark this place as anything at all but a misty 
void. In the direction that seems to be west, an occasional shimmer of 
scarlet or cerulean flickers for a moment in a vague arch shape before fading.
*Description_END
;        
;arch     
ITEM 0 60 VAL2=3301 
;                 
IFPREVERB EXAM 0
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The misty arch shape flickers in and out of existence as you watch.
ENDIF
