NUMBER 3301 
NAME Miasma 
REGION 15                                                           
CHANNEL 72 
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
EXIT E 3302                
EXIT N 3304      
MONSTER_GROUP 45
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
A semi-solid stairway rises from the mist as if carved from it, its upper 
steps shrouded in a wreath of silvery, pulsing light. A burnished gold 
railing spirals along beside the stair, with no visible means of support. 
Outside the circle of light cast from above, the mist shimmers and changes 
color constantly with no seeming pattern to it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
CALL 19
;     
;stair
ITEM 0 81 VAL2=3305
;railing
ITEM 1 1050
;mist
ITEM 2 451 
;         
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
Silvery tendrils twist around each other into chains and cables supporting 
a stairway that seems to be carved of mist. It extends up out of sight, 
disappearing into the gathering mist far above you.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The mist pulses and swirls occasionally flaring brightly in a rainbow of 
colors. It both obscures and is transparent, allowing you to catch glimpses 
of things that simply shouldn't be there.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB EXAM 2
  RANDOM DUMMY1 1 5 0
  IFVAR DUMMY1 = 1
    ECHO PLAYER A disembodied head floats by, laughing uproariously.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY1 = 2
    ECHO PLAYER Through the mist, you see a battle of epic proportions. As you watch, the mist 
    ECHO PLAYER swirls, and the battleground is gone.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY1 = 3
    ECHO PLAYER A crystal tower rises against a midnight sky, reflecting the light of a myriad shooting stars.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY1 = 4
    ECHO PLAYER Ten black-robed mages stand, each at an intersection point of a pentagram 
    ECHO PLAYER inscribed in light. In the center stands a radiant woman robed in white 
    ECHO PLAYER and silver conversing with a demon.
  ENDIF
  IFVAR DUMMY1 = 5
    ECHO PLAYER A single mage stands, his black robes a stark contrast to the shimmering 
    ECHO PLAYER mists. As he raises his arms, a single crystal on the ground before him 
    ECHO PLAYER begins to grow, forming itself into a crystal spire that catches the 
    ECHO PLAYER flashes of light.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB E -1
   DISBAND
ENDIF
