REGION 15
CHANNEL 72    
ASTRAL
;
*DESCRIPTION_START
The stairs end abruptly at a wide landing with burnished gold railings. A 
flight of black marble stairs rises to the right. A fine silver chain is 
hooked to posts on either side, blocking access to the steps. Directly 
across from the stairway leading down is a boarded window.
