;window
ITEM 3 475
;chain
ITEM 4 332 ADJ1=657 ADJ2=292
;
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 3
Oddly, the boards are inside the window, though the glass looks far too heavy 
to break easily. A slot about 4 inches high is cut out of the bottom of the 
glass, and a round metal grille is set into its center. A small sign in the 
corner reads, "Continuous Showings -- Tickets: 5 Gold."
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB CLIMB 1    
