NUMBER 3307 
NAME Sentry Mound
REGION 15
CHANNEL 72
ASTRAL
EXIT S 3304
EXIT N 3308
CALL 19
*DESCRIPTION_START
Several thin trees stand sentry over a small mound, their roots sunk in a 
foot of fetid water. Above their straggly branches, the sky is a sickly pale 
yellow with glowering gray clouds. At the base of the mound, the water 
gives way to oozing mud that is nearly indistinguishable from the scum that 
covers the small pool's surface. The eerie stillness is broken by an 
occassional plop as a bubble rises to the top of the thick water and pops.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;mound
ITEM 0 916
;pool
ITEM 1 324
;tree
ITEM 2 881 ADJ1=628
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 0
At first glance, the mound appears to be no more than a small upheaval of 
the firmament. Closer inspection shows that the top of the mound is sheared 
off to leave a flat surface that has been polished till it gleams darkly even 
in this gloom. Embedded below the surface is the stylized depiction of a 
single rose being shredded by a disembodied left hand.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 2
The shape of the trees is disturbingly familiar, branches raised like arms 
mid-incantation. The movement of the air stirs the outermost tips of the 
branches, reminding you of fingers tracing the patterns of a magical spell.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 1
The scummy surface of the pool stirs and bubbles uneasily, wafting sulfurous 
fumes into the air. The mud around the pool is littered with the skeletons of 
small animals, mixed here and there with bones that appear to have come from 
creatures much larger than birds or rabbits.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFTOUCH 0
  CLEARVERB
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 30 The mound gleams darker for a moment, then flares brightly.
  ECHO OTHERS As %n approaches the mound, it gleams darker, then suddenly flares brightly.
ENDIF
IFTOUCH 1
  CLEARVERB
  DAMAGEPLR BURN 30 The water in the pool bubbles fiercely, eating at your skin.
  ECHO OTHERS As %n comes in contact with the pool, it bubbles fiercely, eating at %i skin.
ENDIF
