NUMBER 3318 
NAME Room Crystal Tower, Courtyard
REGION 15
CHANNEL 72
ASTRAL
EXIT W 3319
EXIT E 3320
MONSTER_GROUP 46
CALL 19                                                              
ITEM 0 773 val2=3321                                        
*DESCRIPTION_START
In stark contrast to the misty chaos outside the tower gates, the courtyard 
is laid out in precise patterns. Low walls of fieldstone outline raised beds 
of herbs and flowers, every specimen carefully labeled. A flagstone walkway 
leads both east and west and to the open front doors.
*DESCRIPTION_END
